sequenceDiagram
participant S as server
participant B as broker
participant Y as yggdrasil
participant D as DBus
participant W as workerEcho

S ->> B: data/in {IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker}
B ->> Y: data/in {IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker}
Y ->> D: Dispatcher method
D ->>+ W: data/in {IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController}
Note right of W: echo process
W ->> D: Worker Event {IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode}
D ->> Y: Worker Event {IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream}
W ->> D: Worker Event {IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController}
D ->> Y: Worker Event {IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController}
W ->>- D: data/out  message: {IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic}
D ->> Y: data/out  message: {IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController}
Y ->> B: data/out {IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode}
B ->> S: data/out {IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController}
W ->> D: Worker Event {IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream}
D ->> Y: Worker Event {IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController}
W ->> D: .Propierties Update DispatchedAt feature
D ->> Y: .Propierties Update DispatchedAt feature
Note right of Y: Update status of workers
Y ->> B: control/out {IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode}}
B ->> S: control/out {IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic}
